            <title>[SOLR-4798] shard splitting does not respect router (docs with a compositeId may not go to correct shard)</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-4798</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Lowest level shard splitting code needs to somehow use the router for the collection.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
